<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const randomIntArrayInRange = (min, max, n = 1) =>
  Array.from({ length: n }, () => Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1)) + min);]]></content>
	<description>Returns an array of n random integers in the specified range.  Use `Array.from()` to create an empty array of the specific length, `Math.random()` to generate a random number and map it to the desired range, using `Math.floor()` to make it an integer.</description>
